{"title":"斥孟买的“示威者”","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"斥孟买的“示威者”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿，卑怯的灵魂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁收买了你们？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哙，可怜的蠢才！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少钱一次游行？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道你们的主子只教会了你们这一点儿本领？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道几只西红柿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就算是你们全部的战斗资本？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸而来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬长而去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咄咄，什么行径！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别把你们反帝的先人的脸儿丢尽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不许！不准！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侮辱我们伟大的领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决不容忍！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警告你们的是六亿多中国人民！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不许！不准！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"损害印中友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决不容忍！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警告你们的还有三亿多印度人民！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}